### Hadith 4:81

*Narrated Anas bin Malik*

In the life-time of the Prophet, Abu Talha did not fast because of the
Jihad, but after the Prophet died I never saw him without fasting except
on 'Id-ul-Fitr and 'Id-ul-Aclha.

